query: SELECT r.r_name, COUNT(n.n_nationkey) AS num_nations FROM region r JOIN nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey GROUP BY r.r_name ORDER BY num_nations DESC
SELECT c.c_mktsegment, AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_acctbal FROM customer c GROUP BY c.c_mktsegment ORDER BY avg_acctbal DESC
SELECT p.p_type, SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_avail_qty FROM part p JOIN partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey GROUP BY p.p_type ORDER BY total_avail_qty DESC
SELECT s.s_name, COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM supplier s JOIN lineitem l ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey WHERE s.s_acctbal > 5000 GROUP BY s.s_name ORDER BY num_orders DESC
SELECT o.o_orderpriority, COUNT(*) AS num_orders FROM orders o WHERE o.o_orderstatus = 'F' GROUP BY o.o_orderpriority ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT c.c_name, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue FROM customer c JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE o.o_orderstatus = 'F' GROUP BY c.c_name ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
SELECT p.p_brand, COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_orderkey) AS num_orders FROM part p JOIN lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey WHERE p.p_size BETWEEN 10 AND 20 GROUP BY p.p_brand ORDER BY num_orders DESC

SELECT n.n_name, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue FROM nation n JOIN customer c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE o.o_orderstatus = 'F' GROUP BY n.n_name ORDER BY total_revenue DESC

SELECT s.s_name, SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue FROM supplier s JOIN lineitem l ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey WHERE l.l_returnflag = 'R' GROUP BY s.s_name ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
SELECT p.p_container, AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supplycost FROM part p JOIN partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey GROUP BY p.p_container ORDER BY avg_supplycost DESC

SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM o.o_orderdate) AS order_year, COUNT(*) AS num_orders FROM orders o WHERE o.o_custkey IN (SELECT c.c_custkey FROM customer c WHERE c.c_nationkey IN (SELECT n.n_nationkey FROM nation n WHERE n.n_regionkey IN (SELECT r.r_regionkey FROM region r WHERE r.r_name = 'ASIA'))) GROUP BY order_year ORDER BY order_year
